#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/contact.html:84
msgid "Current Exhibitions"
msgstr "現在の展覧会"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:7
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "よくある質問"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:8
msgid "Quick answers to common visitor, artist, and submission questions."
msgstr "来場者、アーティスト、作品応募に関するよくある質問への簡潔な回答です。"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:23
msgid "How long does it take to receive a reply?"
msgstr "返信を受け取るまでどのくらいかかりますか？"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:28
msgid ""
"We usually respond within 1 to 2 business days. Messages sent outside "
"office hours are handled on the next working day."
msgstr "通常は1〜2営業日以内に返信します。営業時間外に送信されたメッセージは翌営業日に対応します。"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:35
msgid "What should I include in an artwork submission?"
msgstr "作品応募には何を含めるべきですか？"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:40
msgid ""
"Please include your contact details, artwork title, medium, year, "
"description, and at least one clear image. A portfolio and CV/resume can "
"also be attached."
msgstr "連絡先、作品タイトル、素材、制作年、説明、および鮮明な画像を少なくとも1点含めてください。ポートフォリオや職務経歴書も添付できます。"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:47
msgid "Can I contact the gallery about partnerships or events?"
msgstr "提携やイベントについてギャラリーに連絡できますか？"

#: C:/Users/rosha/SDEVGP2/Art_Gallery/app/templates/faq.html:52
msgid ""
"Yes. Choose the partnership, collaboration, or events option in the "
"contact form and include the relevant dates, audience, and proposal "
"details."
msgstr "はい。お問い合わせフォームで提携、コラボレーション、またはイベントの項目を選択し、関連日程、対象者、提案内容の詳細をご記入ください。"

